The goal of libminer is to provide summary of a users library. It is a toy package for testing and learning package development.

## Installation

You can install the development version of skmoose from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("gcperk/skmoose")
```
